old significant implications for school finance reform, NCLB, and the future of intergovernmental relations."--cProvided by publisher.  aDescription based on information from the publisher. 0aEducationzUnited StatesxFinance. 0aEducational accountabilityzUnited States. 0aEducation and statezUnited States. 0aEducational equalizationzUnited States. 0aEducational changezUnited States. 4aElectronic books.2 aMichigan Publishing (University of Michigan)epublisher.40zAccess to the Michigan Publishing online version:uhttps://doi.org/10.3998/mpub.1200038